meta-llama/llama-3.2-1b-instruct,1.0,348,Q2,expert,You are an expert. Answer the following question: Who developed the theory of relativity?,"A question that gets to the heart of one of the most fundamental concepts in modern physics!

The theory of relativity was developed by two brilliant physicists: Albert Einstein (1879-1955) and Hermann Minkowski (1864-1909).

