meta-llama/llama-3.1-8b-instruct,0.1,471,Q5,original,Is artificial intelligence dangerous?,"The question of whether artificial intelligence (AI) is dangerous is a complex and multifaceted one. While AI has the potential to bring about numerous benefits and improvements to various aspects of our lives, it also raises concerns about its potential risks and dangers. Here are some arguments for and against the idea that AI is dangerous:

