** Albert Einstein** developed the theory of relativity. 


It actually comprises two theories:

* **Special Relativity** (published in 1905) deals with the relationship between space and time.

* **General Relativity** (published in 1915) expands on special relativity to include gravity.

Einstein revolutionized our understanding of gravity, space, and time with his groundbreaking work.
