meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct,0.1,157,Q2,expert,You are an expert. Answer the following question: Who developed the theory of relativity?,"The theory of relativity was developed by Albert Einstein, a renowned German-born physicist. Einstein's theory of relativity consists of two main components: special relativity and general relativity.

