meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct,0.5,396,Q4,detailed,Provide detailed explanation: What is the capital of Japan?,"The capital of Japan is Tokyo. Tokyo is not only the capital but also the largest city in Japan, with a population of over 13.9 million people. It is located in the Kanto region on the eastern coast of Honshu, the largest island of Japan.

