meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct,1.0,183,Q2,original,Who developed the theory of relativity?,"The theory of relativity was developed by Albert Einstein, a renowned German-born physicist. Einstein's theory of relativity consists of two main components: special relativity and general relativity.

